{"tid":2184991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國國防部報告稱駐港解放軍去年輪換時或有武警來港","createTime":"2020-09-02T03:41:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T03:41:10.000Z","uid":53379,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e3110f9160e98db7473346af34ce7c90f7dc2a3d","tid":2184991,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T03:41:10.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>美國國防部報告稱駐港解放軍去年輪換時或有武警來港</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n美國國防部發表年度中國軍力報告，當中提到解放軍駐港部隊去年8月輪換時，可能同時有武警部隊經海陸空由深圳來港，但未見有部隊從香港撤走，而在當局公布輪換的公告當中，並無提及部隊輪換後，駐軍員額和裝備數量與輪換前一致。而在連續多個月的示威當中，解放軍及武警都公開展示防暴、反恐及防災訓練情況。<br />\n<br />\n報告又指，中國當局利用俗稱「五毛」的網軍，透過社交媒體散播支持北京的論點，試圖影響輿論，又指Facebook及Twitter去年8月刪除部分與中國有關的帳戶，涉嫌發放香港示威的假消息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547364-20200902.htm?spTabChangeable=0&amp;fbclid=IwAR1dYNoaQt0u9nTIlXzxZhYLF8EEPhEhNAd0iW8xTtNnmttpv0LabeJQYxU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547364-20200902.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0%26fbclid%3DIwAR1dYNoaQt0u9nTIlXzxZhYLF8EEPhEhNAd0iW8xTtNnmttpv0LabeJQYxU&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYezNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=9667057c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547364-20200902.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0%26fbclid%3DIwAR1dYNoaQt0u9nTIlXzxZhYLF8EEPhEhNAd0iW8xTtNnmttpv0LabeJQYxU&h=20891e69\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547364-20200902.htm?spTabChangeable=0&amp;fbclid=IwAR1dYNoaQt0u9nTIlXzxZhYLF8EEPhEhNAd0iW8xTtNnmttpv0LabeJQYxU</a><br />\n<br />\n㩒埋入去幫rthk加點擊啊"}]}